des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us by email: support@hihome.eu

Amazon Alexa and Hihome Smart Home products work together to help you control home devices nice and easy.
You can ask Alexa to turn on, turn off, or dim the light. 
There is no need to go to the switch to adjust your home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap, or Echo Show. 

Connect Alexa to your Hihome Smart products in a few simple steps:
1. Download the Hihome Smart App in Android or iOS App Store;
2. Register your Hihome Smart account in the Hihome Smart App;
3. You need to have some Hihome Smart devices in hand;
4. Configure these devices in the Hihome Smart App and change the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in Hihome Smart Skills;
5. Download Amazon Alexa App from Android, iOS or Amazon App Store;
6. Configure Echo with Alexa App;
7. Search “Hihome Smart" skill from the Alexa App Skills category;
8. Click Enable Skill of Hihome Smart, and you will be directed to Hihome Smart login page;
9. Input your Hihome account username and password, you will be redirected to the success page;
10. Now the setup is finished. 

You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim living room light"
“Alexa, brighten living room light"
“Alexa, set the living room light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
“Alexa, turn on bedroom air conditioner"
